@|bold NAME|@

  @{command.name} - @{command.description}

@|bold SYNOPSIS|@

  @|bold @{command.name}|@ [options] [section]

@|bold DESCRIPTION|@

  Displays various information about the shell.  Information is split up
  into sections.  The follow sections are available:

      SHELL
      TERMINAL
      JVM
      THREADS
      MEMORY
      CLASSES
      OS
      LICENSE

@{command.details}

@|bold EXAMPLES|@

  Display the JVM section:

    @{command.name} jvm

  Display the JVM and OS sections:

    @{command.name} jvm os

  Display all sections:

    @{command.name} -a

@|bold SEE ALSO|@

  @|bold pref/set|@
